/s/aduphf","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/aduphf/mimalloc_new_high_performance_scalable"},{"short_id":"ovw5w7","created_at":"2026-06-03T08:34:46.000-05:00","title":"Domain Expertise Has Always Been the Real Moat","url":"https://www.brethorsting.com/blog/2026/05/domain-expertise-has-always-been-the-real-moat/","score":1,"flags":0,"comment_count":0,"description":"","description_plain":"","submitter_user":"eatonphil","user_is_author":false,"tags":["philosophy"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/ovw5w7","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/ovw5w7/domain_expertise_has_always_been_real"},{"short_id":"boq8pb","created_at":"2026-06-03T08:33:22.000-05:00","title":"Curatube: a distraction free interface for YT playlists to focus on learning","url":"https://curatube-demo.vercel.app/","score":1,"flags":0,"comment_count":0,"description":"\u003cp\u003eYouTube is an incredible resource for MOOCs but the platform itself is an absolute minefield of distractions.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCuratube fixes this by transforming public playlists into focused, interactive courses entirely free from the feed. Take timestamped notes side by side with the video, navigate lectures effortlessly using interactive transcripts.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBest of all, it's open source and designed to be easily self hosted! Looking forward to contributions, suggestions and general feedback. The demo above is read-only.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e:)\u003c/p\u003e\n","description_plain":"YouTube is an incredible resource for MOOCs but the platform itself is an absolute minefield of distractions.\r\n\r\nCuratube fixes this by transforming public playlists into focused, interactive courses entirely free from the feed. Take timestamped notes side by side with the video, navigate lectures effortlessly using interactive transcripts.\r\n\r\nBest of all, it's open source and designed to be easily self hosted! Looking forward to contributions, suggestions and general feedback. The demo above is read-only.\r\n\r\n:)","submitter_user":"metahost","user_is_author":true,"tags":["show","web"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/boq8pb","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/boq8pb/curatube_distraction_free_interface_for"},{"short_id":"ui45py","created_at":"2026-06-03T08:20:13.000-05:00","title":"Mean Hand","url":"https://portfolio.anna-zhang.com/projects/mean-hand","score":25,"flags":0,"comment_count":4,"description":"","description_plain":"","submitter_user":"hush","user_is_author":false,"tags":["design","visualization"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/ui45py","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/ui45py/mean_hand"}]